00:00:42.482 --> 00:00:47.932
=Wild & Fiery=
=Episode 16=

00:00:59.019 --> 00:00:59.780
Don't worry.

00:00:59.900 --> 00:01:01.539
I've had someone remove the posts.

00:01:01.540 --> 00:01:03.019
The attention will die down soon.

00:01:03.420 --> 00:01:04.258
In a few days,

00:01:04.259 --> 00:01:06.099
