00:01:09.259 --> 00:01:09.939
Thank you.

00:01:15.219 --> 00:01:16.060
Zhiyu.

00:01:25.020 --> 00:01:25.819
I...

00:01:26.859 --> 00:01:28.140
I can get engaged to you.

00:01:29.650 --> 00:01:33.379
ظآزListen, the wind chime is ringingظآز

00:01:33.380 --> 00:01:34.261
What do you mean?

00:01:34.262 --> 00:01:35.539
ظآزI wish to forget youظآز

00:01:35.540 --> 00:01:37.500
(I can't tell Zhiyu)

00:01:37.540 --> 00:01:39.539
(that she isn't
Mu Chenzhou's daughter yet.)

00:01:39.859 --> 00:01:41.819
(She might not be able to accept it.)

00:01:42.460 --> 00:01:44.140
The situation right now
is too complicated.

00:01:44.580 --> 00:01:46.819
Only if we appear in front of the media
as an engaged couple

00:01:46.820 --> 00:01:48.340
can we crush these rumors.

00:01:48.979 --> 00:01:51.332
Then no one will point fingers
or gossip about you anymore.

00:01:53.540 --> 00:01:54.700
Shen Jibai,

00:01:55.779 --> 00:01:57.019
what do you take me for?

00:01:57.419 --> 00:01:59.379
You were the one who refused
the engagement before.

00:02:00.020 --> 00:02:01.760
Now things have come to this,

00:02:01.760 --> 00:02:04.179
and suddenly you say
you're willing to get engaged? What?

00:02:05.540 --> 00:02:06.980
Is it fun to toy with me?

00:02:08.900 --> 00:02:09.818
Shen Jibai,

00:02:09.819 --> 00:02:10.900
