00:02:11.300 --> 00:02:13.618
playing the hero who saves the damsel.

00:02:13.619 --> 00:02:16.058
You always appear
at the most critical moment.

00:02:16.059 --> 00:02:17.139
Captain Shen.

00:02:18.779 --> 00:02:20.699
Don't get so immersed
in your bodyguard role.

00:02:20.700 --> 00:02:21.819
I'm not.

00:02:24.219 --> 00:02:25.259
I'm not toying with you.

00:02:25.580 --> 00:02:27.939
The priority right now is
to solve the trouble we're facing.

00:02:28.980 --> 00:02:30.659
I'll always stand by your side.

00:02:33.420 --> 00:02:34.379
Shen Jibai,

00:02:35.379 --> 00:02:36.740
if I wanted to get engaged,

00:02:36.900 --> 00:02:38.819
I would have plenty of options.

00:02:40.420 --> 00:02:41.539
There are many things

00:02:41.659 --> 00:02:44.020
you don't want to explain. That's fine.

00:02:45.180 --> 00:02:46.640
I don't want to hear them either.

00:02:49.659 --> 00:02:50.859
If there's nothing else,

00:02:51.260 --> 00:02:52.180
please leave.

00:02:55.379 --> 00:02:56.419
- Zhiyu, I...
- Out!

00:02:58.475 --> 00:03:02.849
ظآزHow do I live after losing you?ظآز

00:03:02.850 --> 00:03:09.480
ظآزWhen I look up at the distant starsظآز

00:03:10.012 --> 00:03:14.207
ظآزEverything is hazyظآز

00:03:19.420 --> 00:03:20.259
