00:03:20.580 --> 00:03:22.939
there's something
I need you to investigate.

00:03:29.000 --> 00:03:30.920
(It's been a long time
since I came back.)

00:03:31.600 --> 00:03:33.819
(This place still looks the same
as when I was a child.)

00:03:58.580 --> 00:03:59.740
(When I was little,)

00:04:00.539 --> 00:04:02.819
(Mom would often cry
while holding this photo.)

00:04:03.420 --> 00:04:05.259
(Sometimes, I heard her
calling "daughter".)

00:04:05.460 --> 00:04:06.740
(If)

00:04:07.219 --> 00:04:08.900
(the little girl in the photo)

00:04:09.180 --> 00:04:10.699
(was actually her biologocal child,)

00:04:11.779 --> 00:04:14.240
(then I must find out Zhiyu's
true identity as soon as possible.)

00:04:14.619 --> 00:04:16.499
(Only then can I figure out
our relationship)

00:04:17.219 --> 00:04:18.739
(and continue walking forward with her.)

00:04:20.380 --> 00:04:22.859
(I never expected Shen Jibai
to have so many secrets.)

00:04:44.099 --> 00:04:44.979
Stop.

00:04:55.859 --> 00:04:56.700
What's wrong?

00:05:00.219 --> 00:05:01.340
There's something

00:05:02.179 --> 00:05:03.940
I want you to explain.

00:05:04.339 --> 00:05:05.099
What is it?

00:05:06.979 --> 00:05:08.940
You asked me about the pendant before.

00:05:09.620 --> 00:05:10.780
I told you

00:05:11.620 --> 00:05:13.619
it was left to me by my grandfather.

00:05:14.300 --> 00:05:15.659
Originally, there were two of them.

00:05:16.140 --> 00:05:17.460
One for a boy, and one for a girl.

00:05:18.859 --> 00:05:20.979
I want you to tell me

00:05:23.620 --> 00:05:25.499
why this pendant is with you.

00:05:37.739 --> 00:05:39.539
You're not going to tell me

00:05:40.659 --> 00:05:42.820
that we're actually siblings, are you?

00:05:43.739 --> 00:05:45.059
Is that why

00:05:45.099 --> 00:05:46.819
you approached me before
and then rejected me?

00:05:46.820 --> 00:05:47.780
Of course not.

00:05:55.940 --> 00:05:56.940
You're not my sister.

00:05:59.500 --> 00:06:00.539
So

00:06:01.500 --> 00:06:03.580
you've been investigating this
all along.

00:06:04.500 --> 00:06:06.739
That's also why you rejected me.

00:06:09.419 --> 00:06:10.499
This pendant

00:06:11.380 --> 00:06:13.499
was found among my mom's belongings.

00:06:15.339 --> 00:06:17.460
I thought it was something
she left for me,

00:06:17.739 --> 00:06:19.179
so I've always kept it with me.

00:06:20.060 --> 00:06:20.979
I never expected

00:06:21.460 --> 00:06:23.020
that you also had an identical one.

00:06:27.779 --> 00:06:28.539
Zhiyu,

00:06:30.339 --> 00:06:31.819
there are many things

00:06:31.820 --> 00:06:33.099
I haven't completely found out.

00:06:34.140 --> 00:06:36.220
But I hope you can give me some time.

00:06:37.900 --> 00:06:38.979
I promise

00:06:39.419 --> 00:06:41.460
I will definitely
explain everything to you.

00:06:51.620 --> 00:06:52.739
Alright.

00:06:53.979 --> 00:06:55.659
I'll get engaged to you.

00:06:57.419 --> 00:06:58.259
But

00:06:58.260 --> 00:07:00.140
you must tell me the truth soon.

00:07:01.020 --> 00:07:04.059
Because I don't want to marry someone
who is full of secrets.

00:07:04.620 --> 00:07:05.499
Okay?

00:07:07.219 --> 00:07:08.940
Okay.

00:07:13.060 --> 00:07:13.940
(Zhiyu,)

00:07:14.487 --> 00:07:16.208
(no matter who you are,)

00:07:16.539 --> 00:07:18.299
(no matter whose daughter you are,)

00:07:18.940 --> 00:07:20.179
(to me,)

00:07:20.637 --> 00:07:23.557
